data.Name: Chicken Stuffed Peppers
data.Ingredients:
4 bell peppers,
2 tsp. olive oil,
1 medium onion,
2 cloves garlic,
1 1/2 lbs chicken; boneless; skinless; chopped 3/4in,
1 1/2 tsp ground chili peppers,
1 1/2 tsp ground cumin,
1 tsp sea salt,
1/4 tsp ground black pepper,
1 cup [8 oz] (all natural) tomato sauce; no salt or sugar,
2 [~0.67 cups; 5.3 oz uncooked] cups cooked quinoa,
1 cup [8 oz] canned black beans; drained; rinsed,
1 cup [8 oz] frozen corn kernels,
5 Tbsp chopped fresh cilantro,
2 Tbsp [1 oz] fresh lime juice,
1 cup [8 oz] shredded Monterey jack cheese
